Gotify Hook Plugin for Opencode
================================

A plugin that sends notifications to Gotify when important events occur
in Opencode.

Setup
-----
Set the following environment variables:

  GOTIFY_URL   - Your Gotify server URL (e.g., https://gotify.example.com/message)
  GOTIFY_TOKEN - Your Gotify application token

Events
-----
The plugin sends notifications for these events:
  - question.asked
  - question.rejected
  - permission.asked
  - session.error
  - session.deleted
  - session.diff
  - session.created
  - session.idle
  - worktree.failed
  - mcp.browser.open.failed
  - pty.exited
  - vcs.branch.updated

Priority
--------
Events are assigned priorities based on urgency:
  - High (7): session.error, worktree.failed, mcp.browser.open.failed, pty.exited
  - Medium (5): question.asked, permission.asked, session.deleted
  - Low (3): all other events
